The paper discusses the use of robotic systems for cell injection, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper proposes the use of higher-order-logic theorem proving for the analysis of these systems, which falls under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the safety-critical nature of these systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper mentions the automation of the cell injection process, which falls under the category of embedded systems (cs.ET). Finally, the paper discusses the use of formal methods for the analysis of these systems, which falls under the category of computer engineering (cs.CE).
